headline: Inflation Fails To Chill Fed Cut Momentum
summary: U.S. markets hit record highs as inflation remains manageable, keeping Fed rate cuts on track.

headline: How Rising Q2 Sales and Income Will Impact Equity Residential (EQR) Investors
summary: Equity Residential recently reported its second-quarter 2025 results, posting sales of US$768.83 million and net income of US$192.36 million, both higher than the prior year period. While the company completed the majority of its long-running share buyback program by June 2025, it reported that no additional shares were repurchased during the second quarter. We'll examine how Equity Residential's increased quarterly sales and income might influence its investment narrative moving...
